WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.460
Let's make a reservation at a restaurant!

00:00:06.820 --> 00:00:08.620
Thank you for calling.

00:00:08.840 --> 00:00:10.840
This is restaurant Tayama.

00:00:13.740 --> 00:00:16.480
Hello, I'd like to make a reservation.

00:00:18.280 --> 00:00:19.780
Sure.

00:00:21.540 --> 00:00:23.960
For when, please.

00:00:26.180 --> 00:00:28.820
Tomorrow night, at 7:30.

00:00:31.660 --> 00:00:34.040
Okay. For how many people?

00:00:38.080 --> 00:00:39.420
Two people.

00:00:43.280 --> 00:00:46.740
Would you like smoking or non-smoking?

00:00:51.680 --> 00:00:53.760
Non-smoking, please.

00:00:58.080 --> 00:01:01.100
May I have your name and contact information, please?

00:01:04.940 --> 00:01:06.940
My name is Handa.

00:01:10.740 --> 00:01:12.120
You are Mr. Handa, right?

00:01:16.720 --> 00:01:17.400
Yes.

00:01:19.320 --> 00:01:23.280
My telephone number is 012-345-6789.

00:01:30.260 --> 00:01:34.520
012-345-6789, right?

00:01:35.560 --> 00:01:36.600
Yes.

00:01:38.380 --> 00:01:42.980
Mr. Handa, we'll be expecting you tomorrow at 7:30.

00:01:48.240 --> 00:01:49.720
Thank you.

